  <accessrestrict audience="internal" id="aspace_54aaeb6d2b4af0042809927f99f40301">
    <head>Access Restrictions:</head>
<p>Access to Box 2 restricted to members of the Lambda Omicron members of Sigma Gamma Rho Sorority with current ID (List of chapter members in the accession folder.)</p>  </accessrestrict>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_c48f4c02be532cd81fd5d85a2d7002dd">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>The Lambda Omicron chapter of Sigma Gamma Rho was established at Cornell University in 1990.</p>  </bioghist>
